m-mates\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2046}, {\"ngram\": \"the afternoon\", \"from\": 2058, \"to\": 2071}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 22-year-old, who took up the centre of the ring, and his opponent traded combinations as they patiently probed for openings but the judges narrowly favoured Palaam 3-2.\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2246, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the centre\", \"from\": 2103, \"to\": 2113}, {\"ngram\": \"the ring\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2125}, {\"ngram\": \"his opponent\", \"from\": 2131, \"to\": 2143}, {\"ngram\": \"combinations\", \"from\": 2151, \"to\": 2163}, {\"ngram\": \"openings\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2201}, {\"ngram\": \"the judges\", \"from\": 2206, \"to\": 2216}, {\"ngram\": \"Palaam\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2241}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One minute into the second, Gallagher caught Palaam with a right as he aimed to bring parity on the scorecards but this time the Filipino was up on all five judges' cards.\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2419, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gallagher\", \"from\": 2276, \"to\": 2285}, {\"ngram\": \"Palaam\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2299}, {\"ngram\": \"a right\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2312}, {\"ngram\": \"parity\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2340}, {\"ngram\": \"the scorecards\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2358}, {\"ngram\": \"the Filipino\", \"from\": 2373, \"to\": 2385}, {\"ngram\": \"all five judges' cards\", \"from\": 2396, \"to\": 2418}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With a strong final round needed for any chance to win, Gallagher was aggressive from the off in the third round as he chased Palaam around the ring, with his opponent back-pedalling in search of distance.\", \"from\": 2421, \"to\": 2626, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a strong final round\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2446}, {\"ngram\": \"any chance\", \"from\": 2458, \"to\": 2468}, {\"ngram\": \"Gallagher\", \"from\": 2477, \"to\": 2486}, {\"ngram\": \"the third round\", \"from\": 2518, \"to\": 2533}, {\"ngram\": \"Palaam\", \"from\": 2547, \"to\": 2553}, {\"ngram\": \"the ring\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2569}, {\"ngram\": \"his opponent\", \"from\": 2576, \"to\": 2588}, {\"ngram\": \"search\", \"from\": 2607, \"to\": 2613}, {\"ngram\": \"distance\", \"from\": 2617, \"to\": 2625}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But ultimately Palaam also took the third round 3-2 to win by unanimous decision.\", \"from\": 2627, \"to\": 2708, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Palaam\", \"from\": 2642, \"to\": 2648}, {\"ngram\": \"the third round\", \"from\": 2659, \"to\": 2674}, {\"ngram\": \"unanimous decision\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2707}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gallagher was quick to put perspective on the result afterwards.\", \"from\": 2712, \"to\": 2776, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gallagher\", \"from\": 2712, \"to\": 2721}, {\"ngram\": \"perspective\", \"from\": 2739, \"to\": 2750}, {\"ngram\": \"the result\", \"from\": 2754, \"to\": 2764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At the Olympic Games there is no easy opponents,\\\" he told RT\\u00c9 Sport.\", \"from\": 2778, \"to\": 2847, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2837, \"end\": 2846, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9999999789533833, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c9 Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_Sport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2799}, {\"ngram\": \"no easy opponents\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2826}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He's an Olympic silver medalist at 52kg from Tokyo so we knew the quality operator Carlos is, we knew it was going to be a tough fight.\", \"from\": 2849, \"to\": 2985, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2895, \"end\": 2900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.649274574200558e-13, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Olympic silver medalist\", \"from\": 2855, \"to\": 2881}, {\"ngram\": \"52kg\", \"from\": 2885, \"to\": 2889}, {\"ngram\": \"the quality operator\", \"from\": 2912, \"to\": 2932}, {\"ngram\": \"Carlos\", \"from\": 2933, \"to\": 2939}, {\"ngram\": \"a tough fight\", \"from\": 2971, \"to\": 2984}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I thought I performed very well but maybe the scoring was...\", \"from\": 2986, \"to\": 3046, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the scoring\", \"from\": 3028, \"to\": 3039}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know, maybe it was tighter than what the final verdict was.\", \"from\": 3047, \"to\": 3115, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the final verdict\", \"from\": 3093, \"to\": 3110}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He's probably the smallest in the weight category.\", \"from\": 3117, \"to\": 3168, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the weight category\", \"from\": 3148, \"to\": 3167}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can see it, he comes very low and swings over the top.\", \"from\": 3169, \"to\": 3227, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"swings\", \"from\": 3207, \"to\": 3213}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 3219, \"to\": 3226}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's hard to read and it's hard to catch him when he does it.\", \"from\": 3228, \"to\": 3289, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can not take anything away from him, he's a quality operator.\", \"from\": 3290, \"to\": 3355, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 3307, \"to\": 3315}, {\"ngram\": \"a quality operator\", \"from\": 3336, \"to\": 3354}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am just happy to be on this stage, sharing the ring with operators like that - the best in the world - that's where you want to be.\\\"\", \"from\": 3357, \"to\": 3492, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this stage\", \"from\": 3383, \"to\": 3393}, {\"ngram\": \"the ring\", \"from\": 3403, \"to\": 3411}, {\"ngram\": \"operators\", \"from\": 3417, \"to\": 3426}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3451, \"to\": 3460}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While it wasn't the result he wanted, Gallagher added that getting to box at the Olympics was the realisation of his sporting ambition.\", \"from\": 3494, \"to\": 3629, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the result\", \"from\": 3510, \"to\": 3520}, {\"ngram\": \"Gallagher\", \"from\": 3532, \"to\": 3541}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3571, \"to\": 3583}, {\"ngram\": \"the realisation\", \"from\": 3588, \"to\": 3603}, {\"ngram\": \"his sporting ambition\", \"from\": 3607, \"to\": 3628}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am not a loser.\", \"from\": 3631, \"to\": 3649, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a loser\", \"from\": 3641, \"to\": 3648}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I performed the best I could.\", \"from\": 3650, \"to\": 3679, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Grateful to be here, for all the fans, my family, the whole team; I gave them a day out.\", \"from\": 3680, \"to\": 3768, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the fans\", \"from\": 3705, \"to\": 3717}, {\"ngram\": \"the whole team\", \"from\": 3730, \"to\": 3744}, {\"ngram\": \"a day\", \"from\": 3758, \"to\": 3763}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's what it's all about, I am happy to be here, very grateful, living my dream.\", \"from\": 3770, \"to\": 3853, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my dream\", \"from\": 3844, \"to\": 3852}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I'd be more fulfilled if I came home with a medal but this is what I have always wanted to do.\", \"from\": 3854, \"to\": 3948, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 3896, \"to\": 3903}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We sat there watching London [2012] and said,' would you like to box here'.\", \"from\": 3950, \"to\": 4026, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3973, \"end\": 3979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_GAA\", \"score\": 0.9951805183652738, \"rank\": 0.004842821523589654, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_GAA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_GAA\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, 12 years later, I have boxed in the Paris Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 4027, \"to\": 4088, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympic Games\", \"from\": 4064, \"to\": 4087}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a dream come true.\", \"from\": 4090, \"to\": 4114, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a dream\", \"from\": 4096, \"to\": 4103}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have a lot to be grateful for right now.\", \"from\": 4115, \"to\": 4157, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 4122, \"to\": 4127}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although the decisions did not go my way, and I wanted a better outcome, the whole experience is surreal.\", \"from\": 4158, \"to\": 4263, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the decisions\", \"from\": 4167, \"to\": 4180}, {\"ngram\": \"a better outcome\", \"from\": 4213, \"to\": 4229}, {\"ngram\": \"the whole experience\", \"from\": 4231, \"to\": 4251}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am very thankful to be in this opportunity.\", \"from\": 4265, \"to\": 4311, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this opportunity\", \"from\": 4294, \"to\": 4310}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know there is many people around the world who would give their left arm for this position I am in so I can only be grateful.\\\"\", \"from\": 4312, \"to\": 4440, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many people\", \"from\": 4328, \"to\": 4339}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 4347, \"to\": 4356}, {\"ngram\": \"their left arm\", \"from\": 4372, \"to\": 4386}, {\"ngram\": \"this position\", \"from\": 43